Gratia Dei Patris omnipotentie, pax ac dilectio domini nostri Jesu Christi, et communicatio Spiritus sancti sit semper cum omnibus

vobis.² Rz. Et cum homiuibus bonae voluntatis. Quomodo astatis pacem facite.

In the present Ambrosian rite the Kiss of Peace occurs, as at Rome, immediately before the Corn- munion, but this was not its original position.
